{"tid":957833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正妹空服員女兒要上班　白髮父機上陪過聖誕...網瘋：岳父我來！","createTime":"2018-12-27T10:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T10:45:15.000Z","uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0773a9ea1be74ccf15dc747bed8787cff0b39b0d","tid":957833,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:24:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3793/d3793085.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3793%2Fd3793085.jpg&h=e02fdc93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 乘客里奇（Mike Levy）在機上得知哈爾（Hal Vaughan）的故事後，決定來張自拍並分享故事到臉書上。（圖／翻攝Mike Levy臉書）<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n美國1位父親哈爾（Hal Vaughan）因為思念正妹空服員女兒沃恩（Pierce Vaughan），決定搭乘達美航空從佛羅里達（Florida）底特津，以及底特津飛往麻薩諸塞州（Massachusetts）的班機，在機上陪伴女兒歡度聖誕節。哈爾旁邊的男乘客里奇（Mike Levy）也在得知這段溫馨的小故事後，感動地與哈爾合照，並分享到臉書上祝他們聖誕快樂！<br />\n根據Metro報導，當時里奇搭乘佛羅里達飛往底特津的航班時，得知哈爾此趟旅程的目的是陪伴正妹空服員女兒度過聖誕節，讓他決定把故事分享到臉書上表示，「我幸運地在回家的班機上坐在哈爾旁邊」，但她女兒是空服員，不得不在聖誕節工作，因此哈爾決定和她一起度假，共度聖誕節，「多麼棒的父親！」<br />\n▼&nbsp;哈爾有個漂亮的正妹空服員女兒。（圖／翻攝Pierce T. Vaughan臉書，下同。）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3793/d3793086.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3793%2Fd3793086.jpg&h=6ea0db70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n里奇也在貼文標記哈爾的老婆金帛麗（Kimberly），向她表示哈爾一切順利，甚至還在其中一趟的航班上坐在頭等艙內享受。因為根據達美航空的網站顯示，公司員工和「符合條件的家庭成員」都能享有免費和優惠的旅行優惠。沃恩也在事後感謝公司提供的優惠，讓她爸爸可以幸運地完成計畫，同時向里奇感謝「讓我們知道這件事有多酷」。<br />\n許多網友看到這件溫馨小故事後，紛紛在里奇貼文底下祝福沃恩父女聖誕快樂，「很酷的主意，聖誕快樂！」、「太甜啦！」、「你有個很酷的父親」、「簡直太棒了！」、「我也想要這樣的爸爸」，也有網友看到沃恩的照片後大喊乾爹表示，「爸，讓我來陪你們一起度過」。<br />\n▼ 沃恩常常在臉書上分享生活趣事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3793/d3793087.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3793%2Fd3793087.jpg&h=a20adbee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181227/1341752.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181227%2F1341752.htm&d=FVM6g6NACJYo7aJBQQ6zKAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=4ae8e81d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181227/1341752.htm</a>"},{"pid":"76edcb4f4de19213555946a1fa2a6eac947d2adc","tid":957833,"uid":97045,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:27:10.000Z","msg":"睇錯帛金"},{"pid":"59e92f7ea9e22a0bb9dbcfbac45c30a551890ac1","tid":957833,"uid":52727,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:27:59.000Z","msg":"好醜樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f00845892ba3f99b053847056d58dcab19c619","tid":957833,"uid":113929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:28:41.000Z","msg":"正妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cbc27ab91a028a4afd7430dc791a3f8936b4e2f","tid":957833,"uid":156542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:29:51.000Z","msg":"好肥美"},{"pid":"9068b11e6e77b409e140326ebd726859befe31a9","tid":957833,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c03d9e712182abb6d414de569ae527427f912a","tid":957833,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:31:17.000Z","msg":"巨人族"},{"pid":"25480c343346664c7287eaca904828560edc672d","tid":957833,"uid":8269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:31:27.000Z","msg":"正妹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1357e14e9f97c5258b7d6bca398b923d936f16e9","tid":957833,"uid":212246,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:33:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/34a/85f/34a85f3db926ca75a921096d4ec647a7e1a6a634_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2F34a%2F85f%2F34a85f3db926ca75a921096d4ec647a7e1a6a634_n.jpg&h=ae345863&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2